description:
If you have an existing SQL Server table, use this program to whip up a batch of MVC5 goodness in seconds - models, controllers, views (both desktop and mobile versions) and REST API's by simply pointing this app to that table.
      Visit the Project Website for a quick demo/tutorial.
summary: Use this tasty program to whip up a batch of MVC5 goodness - models, controllers, views (desktop and mobile) and REST API's from an existing SQL Table.
title: Lyle's MVC5 FoodTruck
